+----------+
| .emacs.d |
+----------+

  A simple, lightweight, fast configuration for OCaml, Racket and Coq/Agda development,
  and support terminal.

O THE PROGRAMMING LANGUAGE ENVIRONMENT
  o- Racket: racket-mode + racket-xp-mode
  o- OCaml: tuareg + merlin + ocamlformat + utop
  o- Coq: Proof-General
  o- Agda: agda2-mode
  
O AUXILIARY
  o- Treemacs
  o- Darkroom
  o- Company: company-box
  o- Eldoc: eldoc-box
  o- Flycheck: flycheck-inline

